        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Agenda"><a href="#Agenda" class="headerlink" title="Agenda"></a>Agenda</h2><p>This article discusses the SPI-NAND flash memory read operation.</p><h2 id="SPI-NOR-Flash-vs-SPI-NAND-Flash"><a href="#SPI-NOR-Flash-vs-SPI-NAND-Flash" class="headerlink" title="SPI-NOR Flash vs SPI-NAND Flash"></a>SPI-NOR Flash vs SPI-NAND Flash</h2><h3 id="SPI-NOR-Flash"><a href="#SPI-NOR-Flash" class="headerlink" title="SPI-NOR Flash"></a>SPI-NOR Flash</h3>]]></content>
      
      
      
